Draw and win. Guess what others are draw.msgid: Draw and win. Guess what others are drawing and win too! Here is everything you need to know about the game!
msgstr: Рисуй и выигрывай. Угадай, что рисуют другие, и тоже выиграй! Вот все, что вам нужно знать об игре!

Think of a riddle and create a room!.msgid: Think of a riddle and create a room!

Invite your friends and start drawing!.msgid: Invite your friends and start drawing!

Friends have to guess the word from the.msgid: Friends have to guess the word from the picture in the text chat!
msgstr: Друзья должны угадать слово по рисунку в текстовом чате!

The first person to guess your word wins.msgid: The first person to guess your word wins!
msgstr: Выигрывает тот, кто первым угадает ваше слово!

The picture and the answer will go to th.msgid: The picture and the answer will go to the gallery!
msgstr: Рисунок и ответ попадут в галерею!
